    "text": "EXTRAORDINARY ANNOUNCEMENT\nOPUS GLOBAL Nyilvánosan Működő Részvénytársaság (in English: OPUS GLOBAL Public Limited\nCompany) (registered seat: 59 Andrássy Road, Budapest 1062, Hungary; company registration\nnumber: 01-10-042533; hereinafter referred to as: ' Company ') hereby informs the Esteemed Investors that based on the application submitted by the Company, the Company Registry Court of Budapest-Capital Regional Court, on the 18 th July 2024 by its decision Cg.01-10-042533/492, has ordered the registration of the share capital decrease 1 decided by the Resolution No. 7/2024 (IV.24.) of the General Meeting, and the registration of the related amendment of the Articles of Association of the Company.\nAfter the registration of the share capital decrease, the Company continues its operation with the share capital of HUF 17,459,481,700. -, i.e. seventeen billion four hundred and fifty-nine million four hundred and eighty-one thousand seven hundred Hungarian forints. Following the registration of the share capital decrease, the share capital of the Company consists of a total of 698,379,268 shares.\nThe Company hereby publishes its Articles of Association in-effect in accordance with the concerning regulation.\nBudapest, 19 th July 2024\nOPUS GLOBAL Plc.\n1 https://www.bet.hu/newkibdata/129065056/OG_rendkivuli_tajekoztatas_tokeleszallitas_elso_kozzetetel__20240509_ENG.pdf https://www.bet.hu/newkibdata/129083111/OG_rendkivuli_tajekoztatas_tokeleszallitas_masodik_kozzetetel__20240613_ENG . pdf\nOPUSGLOBALNyrt. tel.:+3614330700\n1062Budapest,Andrássyút59.. e-mail:info@opusglobal.hu\nCg.:01-10-042533 www.opusglobal.hu\nAttachments\nOriginal Link Original Document Permalink Disclaimer\nOpus Global Nyrt. published this content on 19 July 2024 and is solely responsible for the information contained therein. Distributed by Public , unedited and unaltered, on 19 July 2024 07:08:04 UTC .\nShare © Publicnow - 2024",
